node.text:
No day is ever the same @zwfmiami especially when @carrollcity stops by to film his smash show #ConversationsWithCarroll and as you can tell its always a blast when the gang gets toegther inc. @mariowildlife & @mariazwfmiami. 

PR: @mattdillon1983 
____
Book your experience today:

TUG OF WAR WITH BIG CAT EXPERIENCE
So you think you’re tougher than a tiger? Come experience the awesome power of some of the ZWF’s biggest residents in a tug-of-war challenge you won’t soon forget!

18+ Only. 10 minute session.

$150.00 Ages (18+) 
$120.00 Ages (18+ Group of 6 or more) 

All prices exclude tax and gratuity.
Does not include General Wildlife Experience.

node.text:
Our VP, Director & Co-Founder @mariazwfmiami is this weeks guest on friend to @zwfmiami @carrollcity’ show #ConversationsWithCarroll. 🎙 🎥 
___
They talk the journey to creation of our magical place, @mariowildlife, have some fun with our animal ambassadors including dinner with @limbanizwf and so much more in this exciting new episode. 
____
Catch premiere today at NOON EST via #SwipeUp in stories and show the love in comments below 👇.
_____
PR: @mattdillon1983

node.title: Ready for some @limbanizwf dinner time fun?

node.text:
Join us for an unforgettable 5- hour guided experience, that will completely sweep you off your feet! Spend the day interacting with an array of stunning wildlife, catered lunch, jungle music and much more that will transport you to another world! This incredible experience will surely fulfill your bucket list of dreams.
 
ZWF VIP Jungle Experience package includes:
General Wildlife Experience
Animal Presentations
Feline Experience
Primate Experience
Owl Encounter
Catered Lunch (1 hour)
Sloth Encounter
Tamandua Encounter
Watch Limbani paint (No interaction)
Big Cat Photo (Cougar)
#ZWFMiami
#Chimpanzee
#wildlifeadventure 

🎥 @alexis_canovas
@mariowildlife 
@limbanizwf 
@mariazwfmiami
@mattdillon1983

____
Catch premiere today at NOON EST via #SwipeUp in stories and show the love in comments below 👇.
_____
PR: @mattdillon1983
